name: Macee khalid

bio: Macee Khalid is a renowned expert in the field of technology and innovation.With over 20 years of experience,He has worked with top companies and organizations to drive growth and success.Macee is highly sought-after speaker and has given talks at conferences and events around the world.He is also the author of several bestselling books on technology and innovation.
